[
  {
    "startTime": 12.539,
    "endTime": 15.888,
    "text": "So what do you think about all this, Charlie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.888,
    "endTime": 17.471,
    "text": "Come on, come on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.576,
    "endTime": 20.867,
    "text": "What do you mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.867,
    "endTime": 22.627000000000002,
    "text": "Working the backside,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.627,
    "endTime": 25.894,
    "text": "being here in the asshole of nowhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.894,
    "endTime": 28.136,
    "text": "I like working the horses."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.136,
    "endTime": 29.685,
    "text": "What's this one's name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.685,
    "endTime": 31.435,
    "text": "Lean On Pete."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.488,
    "endTime": 36.516,
    "text": "Here'snumber six,  Lean On Pete."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.517,
    "endTime": 37.716,
    "text": "He won, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.716,
    "endTime": 39.291000000000004,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.291,
    "endTime": 40.747,
    "text": "Look, if we're gonna be working together,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.747,
    "endTime": 42.408,
    "text": "you gotta get some manners."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.408,
    "endTime": 43.827,
    "text": "And you gotta chew your food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.827,
    "endTime": 46.176,
    "text": "What does your mom say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.176,
    "endTime": 48.926,
    "text": "I don't know, I don't know her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.93,
    "endTime": 52.848,
    "text": "Well, does your dad have any manners?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.848,
    "endTime": 54.747,
    "text": "I don't know, I guess I haven't really noticed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.747,
    "endTime": 56.736,
    "text": "You gonna be okay on your own today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.736,
    "endTime": 57.568,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.569,
    "endTime": 59.854,
    "text": "Did your mom leave you or something?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.854,
    "endTime": 60.687,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.717,
    "endTime": 66.426,
    "text": "Hey Pete, how you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.573,
    "endTime": 69.916,
    "text": "Can't get attached to the horse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.277,
    "endTime": 73.325,
    "text": "Why not?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.325,
    "endTime": 76.736,
    "text": "They're here to race  and nothing else."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.736,
    "endTime": 78.51700000000001,
    "text": "Lean On Pete finished last."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.517,
    "endTime": 80.146,
    "text": "Listen kid, things are changing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.147,
    "endTime": 81.23700000000001,
    "text": "What do you mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.237,
    "endTime": 82.295,
    "text": "I'm selling him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.296,
    "endTime": 84.57600000000001,
    "text": "He's not a pet, he's just a horse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.576,
    "endTime": 86.71,
    "text": "I'll buy him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.72,
    "endTime": 87.488,
    "text": "With what money?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.488,
    "endTime": 88.629,
    "text": "And where you gonna keep him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.629,
    "endTime": 90.46000000000001,
    "text": "Not in my stalls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.36,
    "endTime": 92.693,
    "text": "Come on, Pete."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.96,
    "endTime": 96.377,
    "text": "I'm gonna get us out of here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.349,
    "endTime": 101.36,
    "text": "My horse needs water, do you mind if I get some?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.36,
    "endTime": 102.309,
    "text": "Who's there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.309,
    "endTime": 104.476,
    "text": "It's a kid with a horse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.589,
    "endTime": 108.28999999999999,
    "text": "Give me my money!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.29,
    "endTime": 109.47000000000001,
    "text": "I'm sorry Charlie,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.47,
    "endTime": 110.64,
    "text": "but I need to call someone for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.64,
    "endTime": 111.888,
    "text": "Just give me a number."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.888,
    "endTime": 113.128,
    "text": "There is nobody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.128,
    "endTime": 113.961,
    "text": "Charlie!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.688,
    "endTime": 120.349,
    "text": "When you don't have anywhere else to go,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.349,
    "endTime": 122.459,
    "text": "you're kinda stuck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.459,
    "endTime": 124.459,
    "text": "Do you guys think I could get a job around here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.459,
    "endTime": 126.739,
    "text": "Yeah, there's a lot of jobs for homeless kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.739,
    "endTime": 129.739,
    "text": "I'm not homeless."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.739,
    "endTime": 131.939,
    "text": "So you're a runaway? No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.939,
    "endTime": 134.358,
    "text": "Okay Charlie, where are your parents?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.579,
    "endTime": 142.912,
    "text": "You gonna get on him next?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.368,
    "endTime": 147.35,
    "text": "He's not for riding."
  }
]